23/05/2003
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- The Macedonian Labour Union Association plans to participate in next year's local elections, according to a report Thursday (22 May) in the newspaper <I>Dnevnik</I>. The daily quoted organisation leader Vanco Muratovski, who said the union association would no longer pledge support to any political party but would nominate its own mayoral candidates. (Dnevnik - 22/05/03)
